data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! Introducing a truly unique opportunity to own a stunning LAKEFRONT property in a GATED community that boasts breathtaking beauty and serenity. Nestled on a PREMIUM LOT, this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home offers an awesome retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. The home itself is a blank canvas, awaiting your personal touch to TRANSFORM it into your dream home. While some remodeling is needed, the potential for this property is truly limitless. With its prime location on the lakefront, you'll enjoy gorgeous VIEWS of the water while sipping your morning coffee on your front deck and relish in the peace and quiet of this lake community. Step outside and take in the beauty of the lush, green landscape that surrounds you. Spend your days lounging by the water's edge, taking in the SERENITY of the lake, enjoy a refreshing swim, or spend the day fishing, playing golf or enjoying an activity at the Clubhouse. The choice is yours! There are also several playgrounds for the kids, basketball and tennis courts and much more. Lake of the Forest is a gated community that provides an added level of security and PRIVACY, ensuring peace of mind for you and your loved ones. And with its picturesque NATURAL BEAUTY and serene atmosphere, you'll feel like you're living in a world apart from the busyness of the city. Don't miss your chance to own this ONE-OF-A-KIND lakefront property and create the home of your dreams in this beautiful, tranquil community.
